def_cn: (食品的)最迟销售日期，保质期
def_en: The sell-by date on a food container is the date by which the food should be sold or eaten before it starts to decay.

def_cn: 不再有效的;不再吸引人的;无用的
def_en: If you say that someone or something is past their sell-by date, you mean they are no longer effective, interesting, or useful.
